Description: A free and open-source collection manager
 Sammelbox is a free and open-source collection manager,
 with a strong focus on simplicity and customization. It provides support for
 fully customizable collections, powerful query functionalites as well as
 synchronization capabilities with Android enabled devices.
 Please have a look at Sammelbox.org for a full feature list and documentation. 
 In a nutshell, the key features include:
 * Free and Open-Source (GPLv3 licensed)
 * Simple, fast and powerful collection management
 * Support for fully customized collections based on a variety of different field types
 * Based on a standardized database which can be used even without Sammelbox
 * Search & filter using the power of native SQL queries, but with an easy to use front-end
 * Synchronization with mobile devices
 * Import & export of your collections
 * Platform independent through the use of Java
